China and the US have been waging a trade war for more than a year, in which they impose tariffs on each other. The dispute between the two countries has negative effects on the world economy and raises fears of a recession in the global economy. Washington is using tariffs to try to get Beijing to change its trade practices and reduce China&#39;s trade surplus with the US.
